{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-index-js","path":"/masters-thesis/","result":{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Ansin","description":"Ansin's portfolio","url":"https://imyentsen.github.io","author":"Ansinlau","twitter":"Ansinlau","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"a99bc36f-18ea-5bff-a3d0-03d398520b5b","html":"<h2>How to enhance the capabilities of investment professionals in socially responsible investing?</h2>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 70.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"an overview of the themes in socially responsible investing\" title src=\"/static/05c804cd8c8ffca3969e498fbed3721e/e8950/sri.png\" srcset=\"/static/05c804cd8c8ffca3969e498fbed3721e/0b533/sri.png 500w,\n/static/05c804cd8c8ffca3969e498fbed3721e/00d43/sri.png 1000w,\n/static/05c804cd8c8ffca3969e498fbed3721e/e8950/sri.png 2000w,\n/static/05c804cd8c8ffca3969e498fbed3721e/14586/sri.png 2314w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Socially responsible investors: those who value sustainability and impact made by their investment and engagement. These are the three core themes: Environment, Society, and Governance. For more info, visit the United Nation&apos;s <a href=\"https://www.unpri.org/an-introduction-to-responsible-investment/what-is-responsible-investment/4780.article\" target=\"blank\">Principles for Responsible Investment website</a>.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>The concept of socially responsible investing has raised awareness among investment professionals. The enterprises want to be more competitive in attracting investment by demonstrating outstanding performance in their social and environmental sustainability. On the other hand, those investors who value sustainability and impact are also keen to figure out an effective way to manage and track the data from the supply chains of their investee. </p>\n<p>However, there are still many practical difficulties that limit the capability of them to take real actions. One of which is the variety of reporting standards in sustainability performance that constrains their capability to make a comparison of the potential portfolio companies.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 48.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"work ahead oy\" title src=\"/static/66e39ad7b7dcbf4f54456a3ad4b592f5/e8950/workahead.png\" srcset=\"/static/66e39ad7b7dcbf4f54456a3ad4b592f5/0b533/workahead.png 500w,\n/static/66e39ad7b7dcbf4f54456a3ad4b592f5/00d43/workahead.png 1000w,\n/static/66e39ad7b7dcbf4f54456a3ad4b592f5/e8950/workahead.png 2000w,\n/static/66e39ad7b7dcbf4f54456a3ad4b592f5/14586/workahead.png 2314w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Work Ahead Oy, a Finnish startup dedicated to offering novel onsite surveying solutions for enterprises to understand and enhance the working condition and human rights in their supply chains</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h3>Research Question</h3>\n<p>This thesis examines <strong>how the capability approach and constructive design can enhance the capabilities of investment professionals in socially responsible investing</strong>. In order to answer this question, this thesis employed a constructive design process iterated through cycles of prototyping and validation in coordination with Work Ahead, a Finnish startup that develops software for businesses to enhance ethics and sustainability performance in supply chains. </p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 64.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"basic concept of constructive design\" title src=\"/static/3227fee5a05c14d67a8b577be3f10201/e8950/constructive.png\" srcset=\"/static/3227fee5a05c14d67a8b577be3f10201/0b533/constructive.png 500w,\n/static/3227fee5a05c14d67a8b577be3f10201/00d43/constructive.png 1000w,\n/static/3227fee5a05c14d67a8b577be3f10201/e8950/constructive.png 2000w,\n/static/3227fee5a05c14d67a8b577be3f10201/8126d/constructive.png 2316w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Constructive Design, where the research and design methods lay. Throughout the iterations of construction process, I gathered rich research data and built up design outcome from scratch to hi-fidelity mockup.</figcaption>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1736px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 70.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"the capability approach in design\" title src=\"/static/ba058e6326e6c128907e22e4002ae259/ab40b/ca.png\" srcset=\"/static/ba058e6326e6c128907e22e4002ae259/0b533/ca.png 500w,\n/static/ba058e6326e6c128907e22e4002ae259/00d43/ca.png 1000w,\n/static/ba058e6326e6c128907e22e4002ae259/ab40b/ca.png 1736w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1736px) 100vw, 1736px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The Capability Approach, another theoretical framework of this research. The approach, mainly developed by Nobel laureate Amartya Sen and Martha Nussbaum, was introduced into design research as a way to shift the focus from the utilitarian values, such as happiness and user satisfaction.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h3>Data and Methods</h3>\n<p>Throughout the research, 18 participants (investment professionals, consultants, and core members of Work Ahead) were recruited for interviews and tests. Moreover, a workshop was organized at the annual conference of European Business Angels Network 2019 in Helsinki for gathering feedback from investment professionals.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1736px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 69.19999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"prototyping and testing\" title src=\"/static/9e4c94cf1f1c1fe5f548740d0f87583e/ab40b/method.png\" srcset=\"/static/9e4c94cf1f1c1fe5f548740d0f87583e/0b533/method.png 500w,\n/static/9e4c94cf1f1c1fe5f548740d0f87583e/00d43/method.png 1000w,\n/static/9e4c94cf1f1c1fe5f548740d0f87583e/ab40b/method.png 1736w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1736px) 100vw, 1736px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Prototyping and testing: the thesis employed the methods in user-centered design, but try to shift the focus from usability to capability.</figcaption>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1736px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"workshop\" title src=\"/static/34d8f880e1294efcf4a0e9891d585e4c/ab40b/workshop.png\" srcset=\"/static/34d8f880e1294efcf4a0e9891d585e4c/0b533/workshop.png 500w,\n/static/34d8f880e1294efcf4a0e9891d585e4c/00d43/workshop.png 1000w,\n/static/34d8f880e1294efcf4a0e9891d585e4c/ab40b/workshop.png 1736w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1736px) 100vw, 1736px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Workshop: a workshop was organized at the annual conference of European Business Angels Network 2019 in Helsinki for gathering feedback from investment professionals</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h3>Data Synthesis</h3>\n<p>Data synthesis helps designers to embed the raw data gathered into the context for design. In order to make sense of the enormous amount of qualitative data from the interviews, the tests, the workshop, and the desktop research, I synthesized the data into useful and communicable information by using a combination of visualized mapping techiques based on mental model diagram, POINT analysis, and affinity diagram.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1736px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 67.19999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"data synthesis\" title src=\"/static/8b22c10c50b512b346bb1c9c91f1bb22/ab40b/synthesis.png\" srcset=\"/static/8b22c10c50b512b346bb1c9c91f1bb22/0b533/synthesis.png 500w,\n/static/8b22c10c50b512b346bb1c9c91f1bb22/00d43/synthesis.png 1000w,\n/static/8b22c10c50b512b346bb1c9c91f1bb22/ab40b/synthesis.png 1736w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1736px) 100vw, 1736px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Data synthesis helps designers to embed the raw data gathered into the context for design.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>My thesis dived into this sophisticated issue with designerly and sociological perspectives. I helped Work Ahead to identify the key stakeholders in this scenario, their touchpoints, and the design opportunities. I kick-started the UX/UI design and front-end development based on the research findings throughout the course of design iteration. I validated the ideas with the workable mockups evaluated by high-profile investing professionals.</p>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"a screenshot of the showcase\" title src=\"/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/3acf0/mental_model_2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/41099/mental_model_2.jpg 500w,\n/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/a2510/mental_model_2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/3acf0/mental_model_2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/12609/mental_model_2.jpg 3000w,\n/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/93719/mental_model_2.jpg 4000w,\n/static/c4d596ff1eea0bedada7150974060a7e/5d222/mental_model_2.jpg 5688w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"a screenshot of the showcase\" title src=\"/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/3acf0/mental_model_3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/41099/mental_model_3.jpg 500w,\n/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/a2510/mental_model_3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/3acf0/mental_model_3.jpg 2000w,\n/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/12609/mental_model_3.jpg 3000w,\n/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/93719/mental_model_3.jpg 4000w,\n/static/bc42a2d8b21f2727ea151d6ab9beeba9/5d222/mental_model_3.jpg 5688w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 70.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"a screenshot of the showcase\" title src=\"/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/e8950/Ch5_mental_model.png\" srcset=\"/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/0b533/Ch5_mental_model.png 500w,\n/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/00d43/Ch5_mental_model.png 1000w,\n/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/e8950/Ch5_mental_model.png 2000w,\n/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/1307b/Ch5_mental_model.png 3000w,\n/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/d2c28/Ch5_mental_model.png 4000w,\n/static/4ecf86f1d3b7d26be08eff58f126fbe5/9cc3b/Ch5_mental_model.png 4932w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figure class=\"grid-image\"><div class=\"grid-image-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"cusjourney\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/e8950/cusjourney.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/0b533/cusjourney.png 500w,\n/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/00d43/cusjourney.png 1000w,\n/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/e8950/cusjourney.png 2000w,\n/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/1307b/cusjourney.png 3000w,\n/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/d2c28/cusjourney.png 4000w,\n/static/7aad882f0d4d4882b77fab3340901eec/9cc3b/cusjourney.png 4932w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 141.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"userflow\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/e8950/userflow.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/0b533/userflow.png 500w,\n/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/00d43/userflow.png 1000w,\n/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/e8950/userflow.png 2000w,\n/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/1307b/userflow.png 3000w,\n/static/a2a623f6c1448eb8b291bc33e01c2512/c7443/userflow.png 3488w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</div></figure>\n<hr>\n<h3>Research outcome and discussion</h3>\n<p>The primary outcome of this research is a web-based interactive reporting platform, which visualizes the data of workplace wellbeing survey conducted by Work Ahead. This platform also allows its users to communicate with each other for further engagement. The proposed website design was prototyped iteratively and tested as to whether it would enhance the capabilities for socially responsible investing of its users. The findings revealed that the proposed design should: 1) provide various options for data export and guidance to integrate the results of the surveys to the other relevant data sources; 2) deal with the data insufficiency by offering suggestions on the relevance between data, standards, and frameworks; 3) deliver encouragement and facilitate peer support; and 4) enable stakeholders to cooperate through a better communication channel.</p>\n<p>The design would still require further observation of the actual long-term cooperation enabled by this platform and the capabilities it serves to enhance. As the capability approach functioned merely as an analytical framework, this thesis also sheds light on the future development of epistemology and methodology for applying this approach in the field of design.</p>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"WIP prototype\" title src=\"/static/9ed730300f80382abf7b9c71ef9415b5/e8950/WIP_prototype.png\" srcset=\"/static/9ed730300f80382abf7b9c71ef9415b5/0b533/WIP_prototype.png 500w,\n/static/9ed730300f80382abf7b9c71ef9415b5/00d43/WIP_prototype.png 1000w,\n/static/9ed730300f80382abf7b9c71ef9415b5/e8950/WIP_prototype.png 2000w,\n/static/9ed730300f80382abf7b9c71ef9415b5/e8f1b/WIP_prototype.png 2246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>A version of prototype and the points that marks about where the feedback is.</figcaption>\n<figure class=\"grid-image\"><div class=\"grid-image-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"standards\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f54485ed7fe2b0648ea9f08ae6d26111/3acf0/standards.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f54485ed7fe2b0648ea9f08ae6d26111/41099/standards.jpg 500w,\n/static/f54485ed7fe2b0648ea9f08ae6d26111/a2510/standards.jpg 1000w,\n/static/f54485ed7fe2b0648ea9f08ae6d26111/3acf0/standards.jpg 2000w,\n/static/f54485ed7fe2b0648ea9f08ae6d26111/eec88/standards.jpg 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"summary\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c4bdb86e0dd5497a853474141bb37548/3acf0/summary.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c4bdb86e0dd5497a853474141bb37548/41099/summary.jpg 500w,\n/static/c4bdb86e0dd5497a853474141bb37548/a2510/summary.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c4bdb86e0dd5497a853474141bb37548/3acf0/summary.jpg 2000w,\n/static/c4bdb86e0dd5497a853474141bb37548/eec88/summary.jpg 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</div></figure>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"the landing masthead\" title src=\"/static/de9aac9dfab75293b70c25eccc89dd16/d9c39/cover.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/de9aac9dfab75293b70c25eccc89dd16/41099/cover.jpg 500w,\n/static/de9aac9dfab75293b70c25eccc89dd16/a2510/cover.jpg 1000w,\n/static/de9aac9dfab75293b70c25eccc89dd16/d9c39/cover.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The final mockup</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h2>Endorsement</h2>\n<p>My work was <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yentsenliu/\" target=\"blank\">endorsed by Ilona Mooney</a>, CEO of Work Ahead:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Yentsen worked independently on a complex, novel topic that applied sociological perspectives to impact investing and included building a functional prototype that we tested with high-profile investors. Yentsen’s thesis work kick-started our front-end development, and his work was of such high quality that we could immediately use large parts in our product. As a person, our team describes Yentsen as talented, goal-oriented and very positive.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I received a full grade (5 out of 5) for the thesis by the thesis supervisory committee at Aalto University. The thesis was supervised by Andrés Lucero, Associate Professor of Interaction Design at Aalto University, and advised by Matti Nelimarkka, University Lecturer at the Faculty of Social Science, University of Helsinki.</p>","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"Enhancing the Capability of Investors","path":"/masters-thesis/","category":["UX","UI","Frontend"],"skill":null,"role":["UX Research (interview, workshop, prototyping, experience mapping)","UI Design (Sketch, Figma)","Front-end Development (Html, SASS, React, RESTful API)"],"description":"Data dashboard for socially responsible investors to engage with their investee to promote the human rights in their offices and supply chains; MA Thesis project at Work Ahead, Finland","date":"2019","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":375,"src":"/static/de9aac9dfab